caption: (Translated by Google) I need the phone number that has this out of service  (Original) Necesito el número telefónico el que tiene esta fuera de cervicio

I think your best bet is ordering in and picking up! I ordered the chicken cutlet from there once and picked it up and that was delicious, but ordered a burger to be delivered and it was absolutely terrible.

Delicious! I ordered the lonestar burger with sweet potato fries. The grilled burger was medium cooked, the way I like it. The fries are good and don't taste frozen. The price might see high but it's quality food.
